reviewText:
For the money, a great video....I like "hearing his story", as any fan would. Saw this oringal on a TV special a couple years back. I purchased this for my 8 year old grand daughter who "adores him", but not "old enough to attend a concert, as usually he is performing "outside", and the "environment can get crazy for a young child. Next best thing? this collection of songs & his story.
Now, I do have a "complaint"...I ordered this Video from Amazon "weeks ago". It "was in stock"....Here I am, "nervously waiting" and Hoping it arrives well "before Christmas 2017" as it IS a Christmas gift for my sweet grand daughter". Now, I see on my account page that it "could be delivered "between "Dec. 19 thru January 3rd???? Thats Terrible! I would never had ordered it! Hopefully, it arrives EARLY this week...Come on, Amazon....you can do "better service THAN THIS!. Why did I "order it a "month BEFORE Christmas!
Horrible. What a scam. Don't buy.
A lot of talking. Wanted music
VERY disappointed! The content was a compilation of videos that were available on YouTube. Totally felt ripped off
